==English==

===Noun===
'''Republic of Ireland'''
# A [[republic]] of the [[British Isles]], situated on most of the [[island]] of [[Ireland]], capital [[Dublin]]. Commonly known as just [[Ireland]] or the [[ROI]], independent from the [[United Kingdom]].

